Time Hops

A comedy sci-fi serial in 5 parts by Alan Gilbey and David Richard-Fox.  A scientist mouse called Eek escapes from the future to 1994 and enlists the help of 3 children to save her planet.  First broadcast 1994.

1. Once Upon A Time: A scientist mouse escapes from the future to 1994 and enlists the help of three children to save her planet.

2. Killing Time: The chase is on as the children catapult further back in time and find themselves in deep water. Comedy sci-fi serial.

3. Time After Time: Steph stumbles across an unexpected part of the puzzle to help Eek&#039;s mission to change her planet&#039;s fate.

4. Long Time No See: Time-hopping has brought the children nothing but trouble. Could a dodgy robot really make things better?

5. Time&#039;s Up: The children are convinced that the &#039;man from the BBC&#039; will help them. But is he really what he seems?
